commit.message:
(TARGET_SWITCHES): Include TARGET_CPU_DEFAULT.

(TARGET_CPU_DEFAULT): Provide default value.
(CPP_SPEC): Test TARGET_CPU_DEFAULT too.

From-SVN: r12056
